# Code Structure

The NoteToMP plugin codebase is organized as follows:

## Core Files
- [main.ts](mdc:src/main.ts) - Entry point that registers the plugin, view, and commands
- [note-preview.ts](mdc:src/note-preview.ts) - Core implementation of the preview functionality
- [settings.ts](mdc:src/settings.ts) - Settings model and management
- [setting-tab.ts](mdc:src/setting-tab.ts) - UI for the settings tab

## Assets Management
- [assets.ts](mdc:src/assets.ts) - Manages theme and highlight assets
- [default-theme.ts](mdc:src/default-theme.ts) - Default theme definition
- [default-highlight.ts](mdc:src/default-highlight.ts) - Default code highlighting

## Utilities
- [utils.ts](mdc:src/utils.ts) - General utility functions
- [inline-css.ts](mdc:src/inline-css.ts) - Handling CSS inlining
- [imagelib.ts](mdc:src/imagelib.ts) - Image processing utilities
- [weixin-api.ts](mdc:src/weixin-api.ts) - Integration with WeChat (Weixin) API

## Configuration
- [manifest.json](mdc:manifest.json) - Plugin manifest
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies
- [esbuild.config.mjs](mdc:esbuild.config.mjs) - Build configuration
